nodes.text: The Din pulsar was a pulsar in the Moddell sector of the Outer Rim Territories. Prior to the Battle of Endor in 4 ABY, Din pulsar was documented by Corporal Ractivelle of the Stardust unit as part of a Rebel Alliance report on the navigation of the Moddell sector in preparation for the Rebel Alliance's attack on the second Death Star.

Before the Battle of Endor, the map of the Moddell sector and the accompanying reports were archived in The Rebel Files, a data archive safeguarding secret rebel documents and information. In 34 ABY, The Rebel Files were rediscovered and ultimately given to the Resistance.
Din pulsar was first mentioned in Star Wars: Build the Millennium Falcon 18, a canon magazine first released in 2015 and published by De Agostini.
